      "representative_posted_date": "2026-03-11T04:00:00Z",
      "representative_length": 789,
      "representative_excerpt": "I support the U.S. Environmental Protection Agency\u2019s efforts to reconsider and clarify the Clean Water Act Hazardous Substance Facility Response Plan regulations. Clear and understandable rules are important so that facilities know exactly how to properly handle and dispose of hazardous substances. Making the requirements clearer will help facilities better ...",
