      "representative_excerpt": "\u201cA list of individuals or organizations, including contact information and preferred communication method(s) that need to be notified in the event of a discharge.\u201d The suggestion I would provide for this is more guidance from the EPA on what types of organizations are preferable to notify and in what specific order should these organization types be prioriti...",
