      "representative_comment_id": "EPA-HQ-OLEM-2025-1707-0005",
      "representative_posted_date": "2026-02-26T05:00:00Z",
      "representative_length": 231,
      "representative_excerpt": "I am against easing up regulations. We need clean water and oil spills are dangerous for people and for wildlife. They also hurt the fishing and shrimp industries, as well as tourism. Please keep the regulations currently in place.",
